13 TL
(# Model Catalog) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This file lists every model family and saved bundle used in the project, along with its purpose in the screening workflow.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Text) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- text_transformer: primary transformer-based text scorer for narrative screening; used when the local transformer bundle is available.) Tj
T*
(- text: classical text scorer and fallback bundle; used when the transformer bundle is unavailable or as a stability backup.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Audio) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- audio: primary acoustic screening bundle; the main audio scorer for mood-heavy and speech-derived signals.) Tj
T*
(- audio_spectrogram: secondary audio branch trained on spectrograms; used as a stabilizer when available.) Tj
T*
(- audio_sequence: secondary audio branch trained on chunk sequences; used as a fallback stabilizer until it improves further.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Image) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- image_dl: primary image scorer; the current CNN-based image bundle with stronger augmentation and better diversity.) Tj
T*
(- image: classical image bundle; used as a fallback and stabilizer for face-derived features.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Comorbidity) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- comorbidity: classifier-chain ensemble for joint label prediction; used to estimate co-occurring domain patterns and now blends upstream text, audio, and image consensus.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Supporting Runtime Components) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(These are not final decision models, but they support the screening stack:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- questionnaire scoring: structured symptom scoring from the assessment workspace.) Tj
T*
(- passive biomarkers: typing and phone-camera-derived adjunct signals for low-hardware screening support.) Tj
T*
(- heuristic NLP features: sentiment, emotion, distress phrases, and safety-language cues that keep the app usable when transformers are unavailable.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Practical Priority Order) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The runtime currently prefers:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. text_transformer over text) Tj
T*
(2. audio over audio_spectrogram and audio_sequence) Tj
T*
(3. image_dl over image) Tj
T*
(4. comorbidity after upstream modality consensus is available) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Where These Models Are Used) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Preview scoring in the dashboard) Tj
ET
endstream
